node.title: Top U.S. athletes to watch at Beijing Winter Olympics
node.description: Thousands of the world's best athletes are getting ready for the Beijing Winter Olympics. These top Americans should be on your list to watch.
node.content: ["The 2022 Winter Olympic Games\u00a0in Beijing officially kick off with opening ceremonies on February 4. Here are some of the top Americans to watch as the competition gets underway."]
